ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fexplainer-what-is-rcs-and-how-is-it-different-from-sms-mms-and-ott-apps-124041600745_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Available%20on%20most%20Android%20smartphones%2C%20RCS%20is%20coming%20to%20iPhones%20later%20this%20year.%20Here%20is%20an%20explainer%20on%20the%20messaging%20protocol%20and%20how%20it%20is%20different%20from%20SMS%20and%20Apple%20iMessage%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fexplainer-what-is-rcs-and-how-is-it-different-from-sms-mms-and-ott-apps-124041600745_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fexplainer-what-is-rcs-and-how-is-it-different-from-sms-mms-and-ott-apps-124041600745_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fexplainer-what-is-rcs-and-how-is-it-different-from-sms-mms-and-ott-apps-124041600745_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDon't%20Try%20To%20Bring%20Down%20System%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20In%20Vote%20Cross-Check%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHearing%20petitions%20seeking%20cross-verification%20of%20votes%20cast%20on%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVM)%20with%20paper%20slips%20generated%20through%20the%20VVPAT%20system%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20pointed%20to%20problems%20with%20the%20secret%20ballot%20voting%20method.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20our%2060s.%20We%20all%20know%20what%20happened%20when%20there%20were%20ballot%20papers%2C%20you%20may%20have%2C%20but%20we%20have%20not%20forgotten%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20told%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20counsel%20for%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms.%20Mr%20Bhushan%20was%20arguing%20how%20most%20European%20countries%20that%20had%20opted%20for%20voting%20through%20EVMs%20have%20returned%20to%20the%20paper%20ballots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20go%20back%20to%20paper%20ballots.%20Another%20option%20is%20to%20give%20VVPAT%20slip%20to%20the%20voters%20in%20hand.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20slips%20fall%20into%20the%20machine%20and%20the%20slip%20can%20be%20then%20given%20to%20the%20voter%20and%20it%20can%20be%20put%20into%20the%20ballot%20box.%20Then%20the%20VVPAT%20design%20was%20changed%2C%20it%20had%20to%20be%20transparent%20glass%2C%20but%20it%20was%20changed%20to%20dark%20opaque%20mirror%20glass%20where%20it%20is%20only%20visible%20when%20the%20light%20is%20on%20for%20second%20seconds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Bhushan%20cited%20Germany's%20example%2C%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Datta%20asked%20what's%20Germany's%20population.%20Mr%20Bhushan%20replied%20that%20it%20is%20around%206%20crore%2C%20while%20India%20has%2050-60%20crore%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNinety-seven%20crore%20is%20the%20total%20number%20of%20registered%20voters.%20We%20all%20know%20what%20happened%20when%20there%20were%20ballot%20papers%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Khanna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Senior%20Advocate%20Sanjay%20Hegde%2C%20counsel%20for%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20said%20votes%20cast%20on%20EVMs%20should%20be%20tallied%20with%20VVPAT%20slips%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%2060%20crore%20VVPAT%20slips%20should%20be%20counted.%20Right%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20said%20human%20interventions%20%26quot%3Blead%20to%20problems%20and%20human%20weakness%20can%20be%20there%2C%20which%20includes%20biases%20as%20well%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BMachine%20normally%20without%20human%20intervention%20will%20give%20you%20accurate%20results.%20Yes%2C%20the%20problem%20arises%20when%20there%20is%20human%20intervention%20or%20(a%20human)%20makes%20unauthorised%20changes%20when%20they%20are%20around%20the%20software%20or%20machine%2C%20if%20you%20have%20any%20suggestion%20to%20avert%20this%2C%20then%20you%20can%20give%20us%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhushan%20then%20read%20out%20a%20research%20paper%20on%20the%20possibility%20of%20EVMs%20being%20tampered.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20only%20counting%205%20VVPAT%20machines%20per%20assembly%20when%20there%20are%20200%20such%20machines%2C%20this%20is%20five%20per%20cent%20only%20and%20there%20can%20be%20no%20justification%20in%20this.%20The%20seven-second%20light%20can%20also%20lead%20to%20manipulation.%20The%20voter%20can%20be%20allowed%20to%20take%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20and%20put%20it%20into%20the%20ballot%20box%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Advocate%20Gopal%20Sankaranarayan%2C%20appearing%20for%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20adopt%20everything%20that%20Mr%20Bhushan%20says.%20We%20are%20not%20saying%20that%20there%20is%20any%20malice.%20Only%20issue%20is%20that%20of%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20voter%20in%20the%20vote%20he%20has%20cast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20asked%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20about%20the%20process%20of%20voting%2C%20the%20storage%20of%20EVMs%20and%20counting%20of%20votes.%C2%A0Justice%20Khanna%20noted%20that%20there%20is%20no%20provision%20for%20strict%20punishment%20for%20tampering%20with%20EVMs.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20serious.%20There%20should%20be%20fear%20of%20punishment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sankaranarayan%20said%20voters%20need%20physical%20interface%20and%20verification.%20%26quot%3BAllow%20me%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20slip%20and%20put%20it%20in%20the%20box%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20court%20responded%20that%20even%20if%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20voters%20raise%20objections%2C%20the%20whole%20process%20will%20stop.%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20rational%3F%26quot%3B%20it%20asked.%20Mr%20Sankaranarayan%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%20it%20must%2C%20I%20am%20entitled%20to%20ask.%20I%20am%20a%20voter%2C%20what%20do%20I%20gain%20by%20deliberately%20stopping%20the%20process%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Dipankar%20Datta%20asked%20the%20petitioners'%20counsel%20not%20to%20compare%20the%20Indian%20election%20with%20voting%20in%20foreign%20countries.%20%26quot%3BMy%20home%20state%20West%20Bengal's%20population%20is%20more%20than%20that%20of%20Germany.%20We%20need%20to%20trust%20someone.%20Don't%20try%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20system%20like%20this.%20Don't%20cite%20such%20examples.%20European%20examples%20don't%20work%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Datta%20asked%20Mr%20Bhushan%20if%20there%20is%20data%20backing%20his%20contention%20that%20people%20don't%20trust%20EVMs.%20When%20Mr%20Bhushan%20cited%20a%20survey%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet%20us%20not%20believe%20in%20private%20polls.%20Let%20us%20go%20by%20data.%20The%20problem%20with%20data%20is%20that%20it%20must%20be%20authentic%2C%20not%20based%20on%20opinion%20but%20actual%20performance.%20We%20will%20get%20the%20data%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20counsel%20for%20the%20petitioners%20said%20public%20sector%20companies%20are%20making%20EVMs%2C%20the%20court%20asked%20if%20he%20will%20be%20happy%20if%20the%20private%20sector%20does%20it.%20The%20matter%20will%20be%20heard%20next%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20VVPAT%20and%20What%20Is%20The%20Case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20VVPAT%20--%20Voter%20Verified%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20--%20enables%20a%20voter%20to%20see%20if%20the%20vote%20was%20cast%20properly%20and%20went%20to%20the%20candidate%20he%2Fshe%20supports.%20The%20VVPAT%20generates%20a%20paper%20slip%20that%20is%20kept%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20and%20can%20be%20opened%20if%20there%20is%20a%20dispute.%20Amid%20the%20Opposition's%20questions%20and%20apprehensions%20regarding%20the%20EVM%20system%20of%20voting%2C%20the%20petitions%20call%20for%20cross-verification%20of%20every%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitions%20have%20been%20filed%20by%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20and%20activist%20Arun%20Kumar%20Agarwal.%20Mr%20Agarwal%20has%20sought%20the%20counting%20of%20all%20VVPAT%20slips.%20The%20ADR's%20petition%20seeks%20the%20court's%20direction%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20the%20Centre%20to%20ensure%20that%20voters%20are%20able%20to%20verify%20through%20VVPATs%20that%20their%20vote%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bcounted%20as%20recorded%26quot%3B.%20The%20petition%20says%20that%20the%20requirement%20of%20voters%20verifying%20that%20their%20votes%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Brecorded%20as%20cast%26quot%3B%20is%20somewhat%20met%20when%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20is%20displayed%20for%20about%20seven%20seconds%20after%20pressing%20the%20button%20on%20the%20EVM%20through%20a%20transparent%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20there%20is%20a%20complete%20vacuum%20in%20law%20as%20the%20ECI%20has%20provided%20no%20procedure%20for%20the%20voter%20to%20verify%20that%20her%20vote%20has%20been%20'counted%20as%20recorded'%20which%20is%20an%20indispensable%20part%20of%20voter%20verifiability.%20The%20failure%20of%20the%20ECI%20to%20provide%20for%20the%20same%20is%20in%20the%20teeth%20of%20purport%20and%20object%20of%20the%20directions%20issued%20by%20this%20Court%20in...%20Subramanian%20Swamy%20versus%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(2013%20verdict)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20plea%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713266820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fcq5c2cmg_supreme-court-reuters_625x300_06_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvvpat-evm-supreme-court-we-know-what-happened-supreme-court-flags-ballot-voting-drawbacks-5454005%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hearing%20petitions%20seeking%20cross-verification%20of%20votes%20cast%20on%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVM)%20with%20papers%20slips%20generated%20through%20the%20VVPAT%20system%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20pointed%20to%20problems%20with%20the%20secret%20ballot%20voting%20method.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvvpat-evm-supreme-court-we-know-what-happened-supreme-court-flags-ballot-voting-drawbacks-5454005%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvvpat-evm-supreme-court-we-know-what-happened-supreme-court-flags-ballot-voting-drawbacks-5454005%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvvpat-evm-supreme-court-we-know-what-happened-supreme-court-flags-ballot-voting-drawbacks-5454005%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20York%20and%20other%20states%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20hunt%20down%20wealthy%20remote%20workers%20and%20demand%20more%20tax%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221885%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22remote%20worker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661e552410c6b0cde5efc073%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStock%20image%20of%20a%20remote%20worker.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20York%20is%20using%20AI-generated%20letters%20to%20challenge%20remote%20workers%20moving%20to%20low-tax%20states.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECNBC%20reported%20that%20AI%20is%20helping%20with%20staff%20shortages%20in%20New%20York's%20tax%20department.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20state%20said%20there%20was%20an%20increase%20in%20audits%20in%202022%20but%20a%20decrease%20in%20auditors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2023%2F04%2F18%2Fnew-york-worlds-wealthiest-city-sunbelt-states-growing-fast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillionaire%20capital%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20world%2C%20but%20some%20of%20those%20who%20want%20to%20stay%20rich%20are%20fleeing%20to%20low-tax%20states%20like%20Florida%20and%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20tax%20department%20has%20a%20solution%3A%20AI%20letters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20sending%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20AI-generated%20letters%2C%20mostly%20to%20wealthy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-work-rto-billionaire-ceo-threaten-fire-workers-wfh-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremote%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20those%20who%20require%20a%20change%20in%20tax%20residency%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F04%2F15%2Fstate-tax-officials-use-ai-to-go-after-wealthy-payers.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letters%20could%20help%20beat%20staff%20shortages%2C%20although%20it's%20unclear%20if%20this%20is%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20they%20were%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20reported%20an%20increase%20in%20audits%20in%202022%20but%20a%20decrease%20in%20auditors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20771%2C000%20audits%20in%20New%20York%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20report%20by%20the%20state%20Department%20of%20Taxation%20and%20Finance%20cited%20by%20CNBC.%20That's%20a%2056%25%20increase%20from%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20the%20outlet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20number%20of%20New%20York-based%20auditors%20declined%20by%205%25%20to%20under%20200%20in%20the%20same%20year%20because%20of%20tight%20budgets%2C%20CNBC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221139%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661e558e20b15f0ff4282d38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENew%20York%20City.%3Cp%3EAlexander%20Spatari%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Klein%2C%20partner%20and%20chairman%20emeritus%20at%20Hodgson%20Russ%20LLP%2C%20told%20CNBC%20that%20the%20tax%20department%20is%20using%20sophisticated%20technology%20%26quot%3Bto%20determine%20the%20best%20audit%20candidates%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20wealthy%20individuals%20who%20have%20relocated%20from%20high-tax%20states%20to%20low-tax%20states%2C%20such%20as%20Florida%20or%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20guess%20what%3F%20When%20you're%20looking%20for%20revenue%2C%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20the%20person%20making%20%2410%2C000%20a%20year.%20It's%20going%20to%20be%20the%20person%20making%20%2410%20million%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20City%20is%20home%20to%20340%2C000%20millionaires%2C%20724%20centi-millionaires%2C%20and%2058%20billionaires%2C%20making%20it%20the%20wealthiest%20city%20in%20the%20world%2C%20according%20to%20data%20by%20residence%20and%20citizenship%20investment%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.henleyglobal.com%2Fpublications%2Fwealthiest-cities%2Fglobal-insights%2Ftop-10-wealthiest-cities-world-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHenley%20and%20Partners%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETax%20departments%20across%20the%20US%20are%20using%20both%20human%20auditors%20and%20AI%20to%20examine%20cellphone%20records%2C%20which%20will%20help%20figure%20out%20where%20taxpayers%20are%20spending%20most%20of%20their%20time%20and%20subsequently%20where%20they%20owe%20taxes%2C%20Klein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNew%20York%20is%20being%20very%20aggressive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state%20says%2C%20'Well%2C%20you%20didn't%20really%20move%20since%20all%20your%20TV%20and%20all%20your%20stuff%20is%20still%20in%20New%20York%2C'%26quot%3B%20Klein%20told%20the%20outer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20understand%2C%20the%20wealthy%20can%20buy%20more%20stuff%20for%20the%20Florida%20home.%20They%20can%20buy%20another%20TV.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20of%20location%20is%20not%20uncommon%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20taxes.%20Celebrities%20and%20millionaires%20around%20the%20world%20have%20gotten%20into%20trouble%20for%20filing%20in%20the%20wrong%20location%2C%20seemingly%20with%20the%20intent%20of%20paying%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20notable%20example%20is%20Shakira%2C%20who%20in%20November%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshakira-income-tax-fraud-settlement-remote-workers-digital-nomads-barcelona-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efined%20%E2%82%AC24%20million%20%3C%2Fa%3E(around%20%2426%20million)%20over%20charges%20that%20she%20failed%20to%20pay%20%E2%82%AC14.5%20million%20(around%20%2415%20million)%20in%20Spanish%20income%20tax%20between%202012%20and%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20period%2C%20Shakira%20listed%20her%20main%20residence%20as%20the%20Bahamas%20(where%20tax%20rates%20are%20lower)%20despite%20spending%20most%20of%20her%20time%20in%20Spain%2C%20according%20to%20prosecutors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShakira%2C%20who%20had%20consistently%20denied%20accusations%20of%20tax%20fraud%2C%20said%20at%20the%20time%20that%20she%20had%20chosen%20to%20%26quot%3Bprioritize%20her%20career%20and%20stability%20and%20that%20of%20her%20children%26quot%3B%20by%20putting%20an%20end%20to%20the%20process%20and%20%26quot%3Bthus%20avoiding%20the%20impact%20of%20media%20exposure%20and%20the%20trial%20time%2C%20which%20is%20often%20of%20an%20exhausting%20length.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York's%20Department%20of%20Taxation%20and%20Finance%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-using-ai-remote-workers-fleeing-low-tax-states-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713266646000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661e56dc10c6b0cde5efc0b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-