F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109346623.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EZeenat%20Aman%20had%20advised%20youngsters%20to%20get%20into%20a%20live-in%20relationships%20before%20marriage%20and%20Mumtaz%20slammed%20by%20saying%20that%20she%20shouldn't%20give%20any%20advice%20as%20her%20own%20marriage%20with%20Mazhar%20Khan%20was%20a%20living%20hell.%20Zeenat%20has%20now%20reacted%20to%20Mumtaz's%20comments%20on%20her!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMy%20Home%20State's%20Population%20More%20Than%20Germany's%26quot%3B%3A%20Judge%20In%20Vote%20Method%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sharp%20response%20to%20petitioners%20citing%20examples%20of%20foreign%20countries%20to%20argue%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20ballot%20voting%20system%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20said%20the%20population%20of%20his%20home%20state%20is%20more%20than%20that%20of%20Germany%20and%20that%20%26quot%3BEuropean%20examples%20don't%20work%20here%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20home%20state%20West%20Bengal's%20population%20is%20more%20than%20that%20of%20Germany.%20We%20need%20to%20trust%20someone.%20Don't%20try%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20system%20like%20this.%20Don't%20cite%20such%20examples.%20European%20examples%20don't%20work%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Datta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20appearing%20for%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%2C%20had%20cited%20Germany's%20example%20while%20arguing%20that%20VVPAT%20paper%20slips%20need%20to%20be%20counted%20and%20matched%20with%20the%20EVM%20results.%C2%A0When%20Justice%20Datta%20asked%20him%20what%20is%20the%20population%20of%20Germany%2C%20he%20replied%20it%20is%20about%205%20crores%2C%20while%20India%20has%2050-60%20crore%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20had%20intervened%20to%20say%20India%20has%2097%20registered%20voters%20and%20flagged%20drawbacks%20in%20the%20ballot%20voting%20method.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20our%2060s.%20We%20all%20know%20what%20happened%20when%20there%20were%20ballot%20papers.%20You%20may%20have%2C%20but%20we%20have%20not%20forgotten%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Khanna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20VVPAT%20--%20Voter%20Verified%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20--%20enables%20a%20voter%20to%20see%20if%20the%20vote%20was%20cast%20properly%20and%20went%20to%20the%20candidate%20he%2Fshe%20supports.%20The%20VVPAT%20generates%20a%20paper%20slip%20that%20is%20kept%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20and%20can%20be%20opened%20if%20there%20is%20a%20dispute.%20Amid%20the%20Opposition's%20questions%20and%20apprehensions%20regarding%20the%20EVM%20system%20of%20voting%2C%20the%20petitions%20call%20for%20cross-verification%20of%20every%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitions%20have%20been%20filed%20by%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20and%20activist%20Arun%20Kumar%20Agarwal.%20Mr%20Agarwal%20has%20sought%20the%20counting%20of%20all%20VVPAT%20slips.%20The%20ADR's%20petition%20seeks%20the%20court's%20direction%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20the%20Centre%20to%20ensure%20that%20voters%20are%20able%20to%20verify%20through%20VVPATs%20that%20their%20vote%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bcounted%20as%20recorded%26quot%3B.%20The%20petition%20says%20that%20the%20requirement%20of%20voters%20verifying%20that%20their%20votes%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Brecorded%20as%20cast%26quot%3B%20is%20somewhat%20met%20when%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20is%20displayed%20for%20about%20seven%20seconds%20after%20pressing%20the%20button%20on%20the%20EVM%20through%20a%20transparent%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713266160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-09%2Fjfu4o4tk_bombay-high-court-chief-justice-dipankar-datta_625x300_27_September_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-n