20that%20it%20would%20not%20shoot%20down%20drones%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20despite%20having%20done%20so%20for%20Israel%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20said%20that%20Iran%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-forces-destroyed-iran-missiles-drones-massive-air-defense-battle-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efired%20more%20than%20300%20drones%20and%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20it%20on%20Saturday%20night.%20The%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20France%2C%20and%20Jordan%20said%20they%20helped%20to%20stop%20the%20barrage%2C%20including%20through%20the%20use%20of%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesperson%20John%20Kirby%20was%20asked%20in%20a%20media%20briefing%20if%20the%20US%20could%20also%20help%20to%20shoot%20down%20drones%20over%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKirby%20responded%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20knew%20this%20question%20was%20coming%20too.%20Look%2C%20different%20conflicts.%20Different%20conflicts%2C%20different%20airspace%2C%20different%20threat%20picture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20%26quot%3Bhas%20been%20clear%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20United%20States%20is%20not%20gonna%20be%20involved%20in%20that%20conflict%20in%20a%20combat%20role%2C%20and%20we%20haven't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222058%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20military%20personnel%20display%20a%20downed%20Russian%20drone%20during%20a%20press%20conference.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654f69c236d588dc55cf0207%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20military%20personnel%20display%20a%20downed%20Russian%20drone%20during%20a%20press%20conference.%3Cp%3ESERGEI%20SUPINSKY%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20been%20firing%20drones%20and%20missiles%20across%20Ukraine%20as%20part%20of%20its%20full-scale%20invasion%2C%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-fires-long-range-69-cruise-missiles-ukraine-attacks-isw-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehitting%20and%20destroying%20energy%20infrastructure%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well%20as%20residential%20buildings%2C%20and%20killing%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20the%20response%20to%20Iran's%20aerial%20attack%20on%20Israel%20%26quot%3Bdemonstrated%20how%20truly%20effective%20unity%20in%20defending%20against%20terror%20can%20be%20when%20it%20is%20based%20on%20sufficient%20political%20will.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTogether%2C%20they%20prevented%20terror%20from%20prevailing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20they%20are%20working%20together%2C%20and%20in%20coordination%20with%20others%2C%20to%20prevent%20further%20escalation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelenskyy%20said%20that%20similar%20actions%20should%20be%20taken%20to%20protect%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20Ukraine's%20allies%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20have%20said%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20help%20without%20escalating%20the%20conflict%20with%20Russia.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukriane-nato-deal-should-begin-immediately-lithuania-pm-to-insider-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20world%20leaders%20have%20rebuffed%20this%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20Russia%20will%20escalate%20the%20war%20either%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelenskyy%20said%20the%20response%20to%20the%20attack%20on%20Israel%20also%20showed%20that%20NATO%20members%20can%20protect%20non-member%20states%2C%20and%20could%20protect%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20is%20not%20part%20of%20the%20military%20alliance%2C%20in%20the%20same%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael%20is%20not%20a%20NATO%20member%2C%20so%20no%20action%2C%20such%20as%20triggering%20Article%205%2C%20was%20required%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20alliance's%20collective%20defense%20clause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20was%20dragged%20into%20the%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelenskyy%20added.%20%26quot%3BThey%20simply%20contributed%20to%20the%20protection%20of%20human%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20wearing%20a%20headscarf%20and%20a%20green%20knitted%20top%20looks%20to%20the%20sky%20with%20a%20pained%20expression%20in%20front%20of%20a%20destroyed%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65843994cefc010bea2616ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20woman%20stands%20next%20to%20a%20destroyed%20house%20in%20Lyman%2C%20Donetsk%20region%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20in%20April%202022.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FJorge%20Silva%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EZelenskyy%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20%26quot%3BEuropean%20skies%20could%20have%20received%20the%20same%20level%20of%20protection%20long%20ago%20if%20Ukraine%20had%20received%20similar%20full%20support%20from%20its%20partners%20in%20intercepting%20drones%20and%20missiles.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20is%20running%20critically%20low%20on%20air%20defense%20missiles%2C%20which%20means%20Russia's%20attacks%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20get%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20in%20Congress%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-aid-good-us-economy-defense-industrial-base-republicans-2024-2%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estalled%20further%20aid%20for%20Ukraine%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20past%20six%20months%2C%20preventing%20any%20new%20supplies%20coming%20from%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKirby%20said%20the%20US%20had%20previously%20given%20Ukraine%20%26quot%3Bthe%20tools%20that%20they%20need%20to%20help%20defend%20their%20space.%20And%20unfortunately%2C%20we%20can't%20do%20that%20right%20now%2C%20because%20we%20don't%20have%20the%20Nation