ire%20outside%20Bollywood%20superstar%20Salman%20Khan's%20house%20in%20Bandra%2C%20Mumbai.%20The%20accused%2C%20Vicky%20Gupta%20(24)%20and%20Sagar%20Pal%20(21)%2C%20both%20residents%20of%20Bihar%2C%20were%20on%20the%20run%20after%20the%20firing%20incident%20outside%20Khan's%20house%20at%20the%20Galaxy%20Apartment%20in%20Bandra%20area%20here%20early%20Sunday%20morning.%20They%20were%20arrested%20late%20Monday%20night%20from%20Mata%20No%20Madh%20village%20in%20Gujarat's%20Kutch%20district%20and%20later%20brought%20to%20Mumbai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhat%20About%20Udaipur%20Tailor%3F%26quot%3B%20Supreme%20Court%20Asks%20Amid%20Plea%20Over%20Lynchings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20killing%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fkanhaiya-lal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKanhaiya%20Lal%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0-%20the%20tailor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FUdaipur%2520Tailor%2520Murder%2520A%2520Terror%2520Attack%3B%2520Mourning%2520Wife%2520Explains%2520His%2520Last%2520Days%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehacked%20to%20death%20outside%20his%20shop%20in%20broad%20daylight%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Udaipur%20in%20June%202022%20-%20featured%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Tuesday%2C%20as%20it%20heard%20a%20PIL%2C%20or%20public%20interest%20litigation%2C%20red-flagging%20increasing%20mob%20violence%20against%20minorities%2C%20including%20those%20lynched%20by%20cow%20vigilantes%2C%20and%20seeking%20immediate%20interim%20financial%20relief%20for%20the%20families%20of%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%2C%20Justice%20Aravind%20Kumar%2C%20and%20Justice%20Sandeep%20Mehta%20referred%20to%20the%20Kanhaiya%20Lal%20murder%20and%20asked%20petitioning%20lawyers%20to%20not%20be%20selective%20when%20presenting%20such%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20about%20that%20tailor%20in%20Rajasthan...%20Kanhaiya%20Lal...%20who%20was%20lynched%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked%2C%20to%20which%20Advocate%20Nizam%20Pasha%2C%20representing%20the%20petitioners%2C%20acknowledged%20it%20had%20not%20been%20mentioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20be%20selective%20when%20all%20states%20are%20there...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanhaiya%20Lal%20was%20brutally%20killed%20allegedly%20after%20he%20shared%20a%20social%20media%20post%20in%20support%20of%20Nupur%20Sharma%2C%20an%20ex%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20spokesperson%20who%20made%20remarks%20about%20Prophet%20Mohammad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20the%20counsel%20for%20the%20state%20of%20Gujarat%20said%20the%20PIL%20was%20specifically%20highlighting%20the%20lynching%20of%20Muslims%20only.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20mob%20lynching%20of%20Muslims%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20advocate%20Archana%20Pathak%20Dave%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20can%20it%20be%20selective%3F%20The%20State%20has%20to%20protect%20people%20of%20all%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes...%20you%20have%20to%20ensure%20it%20is%20not%20selective%20at%20all%2C%20if%20all%20states%20are%20there...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Pasha%20countered%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BOnly%20Muslims%20are%20being%20lynched...%20this%20is%20a%20statement%20of%20fact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20be%20cautious%20of%20what%20you%20are%20submitting%20to%20the%20court...%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Gavai%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20was%20then%20postponed%20to%20after%20the%20summer%20vacation%2C%20which%20runs%20from%20May%2020%20to%20July%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%20last%20year%20the%20court%20sought%20responses%20from%20the%20centre%20and%20six%20states%20-%20Maharashtra%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20-%20to%20the%20PIL%20filed%20by%20the%20women's%20wing%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist).%20The%20PIL%20claimed%20a%20lack%20of%20action%20by%20these%20states%20despite%20a%202018%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20directing%20tough%20stances%20on%20hate%20crimes%2C%20including%20lynching%20by%20cow%20vigilantes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20had%20argued%20the%20%26quot%3Brampant%20rise%20in%20mob%20violence%20and%20lynching%26quot%3B%20was%20due%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bgeneral%20narrative%20of%20ostracisation%26quot%3B%20faced%20by%20minorities%20and%20%26quot%3Bnatural%20consequence%20of%20inaction%20by%20the%20State%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20today's%20hearing%2C%20the%20court%20noted%20that%20so%20far%20only%20Haryana%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20had%20filed%20responses%20regarding%20action%20taken.%20The%20court%20then%20gave%20the%20other%20states%20six%20weeks%20to%20file%20their%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20this%20context%20that%20Justice%20Aravind%20Kumar%20asked%20about%20the%20killing%20of%20Kanhaiya%20Lal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713263760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ftjp5qhfo_kanhaiya-lal-murder-case-_625x300_01_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-about-kanhaiya-lal-supreme-court-asks-amid-plea-over-lynchings-5453773%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20killing%20of%20Kanhaiya%20Lal-%20the%20tailor%20hacked%20to%20death%20outside%20his%20shop%20in%20broad%20daylight%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Udaipur%20in%20June%202022%20-%20featured%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Tuesday%2C%20as%20it%20heard%20a%20PIL%20against%20increasing%20mob%20violence%20against%20minorities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-about-kanhaiya-lal-supreme-court-asks-amid-plea-over-lynchings-5453773%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-about-kanhaiya-lal-supreme-court-asks-amid-plea-over-lynchings-5453773%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-about-kanhaiya-lal-supreme-court-asks-amid-plea-over-lynchings-5453773%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chinese%20Couple%20Leaves%20Baby%20With%20Nanny%20For%20%2455%20Million%20Inheritance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20in%20China%20left%20their%20baby%20with%20a%20nanny%20after%20learning%20that%20they%20were%20about%20to%20inherit%20400%20million%20yuan%20(around%20%2455%20million)%20from%20the%20wife's%20ex-partner.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%20(SCMP)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20pair%2C%20who%20disappeared%20afterwards%2C%20left%20the%205-month-old%20infant%20in%20the%20care%20of%20a%20nanny%20whom%20they%20had%20to%20pay%20110%2C000%20yuan%20(%2415%2C000).%20This%20incident%20has%20sparked%20a%20heated%20discussion%20online%2C%20with%20suspicions%20arising%20that%20the%20couple%20might%20not%20be%20the%20child's%20biological%20parents%20and%20may%20have%20exploited%20the%20infant%20in%20a%20scam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Fsocial-welfare%2Farticle%2F3257533%2Fchina-couple-abandon-baby-nanny-after-claiming-they-will-receive-us56-million-inheritance-womans-ex%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESCMP%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20couple%20claimed%20they%20were%20about%20to%20come%20into%20a%20lot%20of%20cash%20from%20the%20wife's%20former%20partner%20who%20had%20died.%20However%2C%20they%20vanished%20without%20paying%20the%20nanny%20and%20have%20been%20gone%20for%20more%20than%20a%20month%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nanny%2C%20surnamed%20Yu%2C%20said%20she%20was%20promised%20a%20monthly%20salary%20of%207%2C000%20yuan%20(%241%2C000).%20But%20despite%20several%20months%20of%20service%2C%20she%20was%20not%20paid%20and%20even%20loaned%20the