ion%20has%20sparked%20a%20discussion%20on%20Chinese%20social%20media%20platforms.%20%E2%80%9CAre%20they%20even%20the%20real%20parents%3F%20Why%20not%20take%20the%20child%20with%20you%20if%20you're%20going%20to%20claim%20a%20400%20million%20yuan%20inheritance%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20one%20social%20media%20user.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20should%20report%20this%20to%20the%20police.%20This%20story%20has%20too%20many%20holes.%20It's%20highly%20unlikely%20her%20ex%20would%20leave%20her%20such%20an%20inheritance%20unless%20the%20child%20was%20his.%20This%20smells%20like%20a%20scam%2C%E2%80%9D%20expressed%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713263580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fn334pc6g_baby-generic_625x300_15_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchinese-couple-leaves-baby-with-nanny-for-55-million-inheritance-from-ex-partner-5454463%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20couple%20in%20China%20left%20their%20baby%20with%20a%20nanny%20after%20learning%20that%20they%20were%20about%20to%20inherit%20400%20million%20yuan%20(around%20%2455%20million)%20from%20the%20wife's%20ex-partner.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchinese-couple-leaves-baby-with-nanny-for-55-million-inheritance-from-ex-partner-5454463%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchinese-couple-leaves-baby-with-nanny-for-55-million-inheritance-from-ex-partner-5454463%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchinese-couple-leaves-baby-with-nanny-for-55-million-inheritance-from-ex-partner-5454463%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tesla's%20global%20job%20cuts%20to%20hit%20China%20sales%20team%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713263570000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109344942%2Cimgsize-63008.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Finternational-business%2Felon-musk-led-teslas-global-job-cuts-to-hit-china-sales-team-report%2Farticleshow%2F109344149.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla's%20China%20job%20cuts%20due%20to%20sales%20decline%20in%20EV%20market%20competition.%20Analysts%20link%20layoffs%20to%20cost%20pressures.%20BYD's%20new%20models%20impact%20global%20deliveries%2C%20leading%20to%20price%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Defending%20Biggest%20Corruption%20Scandal%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20On%20Poll%20Bonds%20Scheme%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20on%20Tuesday%20attacked%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20over%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20and%20said%20that%20the%20he%20is%20trying%20to%20defend%20the%20biggest%20corruption%20scandal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20public%20at%20a%20roadshow%20in%20Kozhikode%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20if%20you%20saw%20his%20interview%20with%20ANI%20yesterday.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20you%20saw%20his%20face%2C%20his%20eyes%2C%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20defend%20the%20biggest%20corruption%20scandal%20on%20the%20planet%20through%20which%20BJP%20has%20got%20thousands%20of%20crores%20of%20rupees%20by%20extorting%20them%20from%20India's%20businessmen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20ANI%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20was%20aimed%20at%20curbing%20black%20money%20in%20elections%20and%20said%20the%20opposition%20wants%20to%20run%20away%20after%20making%20allegations.%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Beveryone%20will%20regret%20it%20when%20there%20is%20an%20honest%20reflection%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20sharply%20to%20the%20Congress%20leader%2C%20Union%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20candidate%20from%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20said%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20should%20be%20the%20last%20person%20to%20talk%20about%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20is%20the%20last%20person%20who%20should%20talk%20about%20funding%20and%20dubious%20sources%20of%20funds.%20We%20know%20Bofors%2C%20we%20know%20all%20of%20those%20scams%20that%20his%20family%20is%20legendary%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20February%20this%20year%20struck%20down%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20and%20said%20it%20was%20unconstitutional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20further%20mentioned%20that%20Prime%20Minister's%20goal%20is%20to%20distract%20people%20from%20real%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why%20sometimes%20you%20will%20see%20him%20doing%20puja%20underneath%20the%20sea%2C%20sometimes%20he%20tells%20the%20people%20of%20India%20we%20will%20bring%20the%20Olympics%20to%20India.%20Another%20time%20he%20will%20say%20we%20are%20going%20to%20send%20one%20man%20to%20the%20Moon.%20He%20never%20talks%20about%20unemployment%20or%20price%20rise.%20He%20protects%20the%20richest%20people%20in%20the%20country%20and%20forgives%20their%20bank%20loans%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20alleged%20that%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20and%20BJP%20are%20keen%20on%20changing%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20RSS%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20trying%20to%20destroy%20India's%20Constitution%20and%20change%20India's%20Constitution.%20The%20Congress%20party%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20are%20trying%20to%20save%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20also%20said%20that%20Agnipath%20scheme%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20it%20will%20be%20abolished%20if%20INDIA%20bloc%20comes%20to%20power%20after%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Agnipath%20scheme%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20the%20brave%20youth%20who%20dream%20of%20protecting%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20plan%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20but%20a%20plan%20made%20in%20Narendra%20Modi's%20office%20which%20has%20been%20imposed%20on%20the%20Army...As%20soon%20as%20the%20Indian%20government%20is%20formed%2C%20we%20will%20immediately%20abolish%20this%20scheme%20and%20re-implement%20the%20old%20permanent%20recruitment%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgnipath%20Yojana%20is%20a%20recruitment%20scheme%20for%20Indian%20youth%20to%20serve%20in%20the%20Armed%20Forces.%20The%20scheme%20is%20called%20Agnipath%20and%20the%20youth%20selected%20under%20this%20scheme%20will%20be%20known%20as%20Agniveers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Agnipath%20scheme%20provides%20for%20recruiting%20youths%20between%20the%20age%20bracket%20of%2017-and-a-half%20years%20and%2021%20years%20for%20four%20years%2C%20with%20a%20provision%20to%20retain%2025%20per%20cent%20of%20them%20for%2015%20more%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713263340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F736bfg6o_rahul-gandhi-1200-_625x300_16_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-trying-to-defend-biggest-corruption-scandal-rahul-gandhi-on-poll-bonds-scheme-5453396%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20on%20Tuesday%20attacked%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20over%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20and%20said%20that%20the%20he%20is%20trying%20to%20defend%20the%20biggest%20corruption%20scandal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww