20overseeing%20the%20case%20said%20the%20mistake%20was%20irreversible%2C%20leaving%20the%20couple%20divorced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Williams%20tried%20to%20undo%20the%20accidental%20divorce%2C%20but%20her%20efforts%20were%20swiftly%20rejected%20by%20Sir%20Andrew%20McFarlane%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20family%20court%20division.%C2%A0He%20believed%20in%20respecting%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccertainty%20and%20finality%20that%20flows%20from%20a%20divorce%20order%20and%20maintaining%20the%20status%20quo%20that%20it%20has%20established.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyesha%20Vardag%2C%20nicknamed%20the%20%26quot%3Bdiva%20of%20divorce%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20of%20the%20ruling%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20bad%20decision.%20The%20state%20should%20not%20be%20divorcing%20people%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20clerical%20error.%C2%A0%20There%20has%20to%20be%20intention%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20person%20divorcing%20because%20the%20principle%20of%20intention%20underpins%20the%20justice%20of%20our%20legal%20system.%20When%20a%20mistake%20is%20brought%20to%20a%20court's%20attention%20and%20everyone%20accepts%20that%20a%20mistake%20has%20been%20made%2C%20it%20obviously%20has%20to%20be%20undone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe've%20heard%20from%20the%20court%20staff%20that%20this%20happens%20a%20fair%20bit%20with%20the%20new%20online%20system%2C%20and%20it%20should%20just%20have%20been%20fixed%20as%20usual.%20But%20here%20the%20husband%20inexplicably%20took%20issue%20and%20the%20judge%20decided%20effectively%20%E2%80%98the%20computer%20says%20no%2C%20you're%20divorced'%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20the%20kind%20of%20decision%20that%20I%20believe%20would%20be%20overturned%20in%20a%20higher%20court%2C%20but%20where%20the%20upshot%20is%20in%20reality%20that%20a%20wife%20who%20wanted%20a%20divorce%20has%20got%20one%2C%20why%20would%20that%20be%20worth%20doing%20in%20this%20case%3F%20That%20means%20that%2C%20for%20now%2C%20our%20law%20says%20that%20you%20can%20be%20divorced%20by%20an%20error%20made%20on%20an%20online%20system.%20And%20that's%20just%20not%20right%2C%20not%20sensible%2C%20not%20justice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713261900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2Fegd972n8_divorce-generic_625x300_06_January_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-couple-accidentally-divorced-after-law-firms-clerical-error-report-5453515%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20mishap%20occurred%20when%20lawyers%20at%20Vardags%20mistakenly%20filed%20a%20final%20divorce%20order%20for%20the%20Williamses%20while%20handling%20paperwork%20for%20another%20client.%C2%A0%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-couple-accidentally-divorced-after-law-firms-clerical-error-report-5453515%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-couple-accidentally-divorced-after-law-firms-clerical-error-report-5453515%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-couple-accidentally-divorced-after-law-firms-clerical-error-report-5453515%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prince%20Harry%20ordered%20to%20pay%201%20million%20euros%20over%20police%20protection%20case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713261853000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109343912%2Cimgsize-747653.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fprince-harry-ordered-to-pay-1-million-euros-over-police-protection-case%2Farticleshow%2F109343912.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109343912.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl