%20in%20sub-zero%20temperatures%2C%20which%20he%20says%20helped%20him%20to%20maintain%20physical%20and%20mental%20equilibrium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chatterjee%2C%20the%20UN%20Resident%20Coordinator%20for%20China%2C%20recently%20released%20a%20documentary%20on%20the%20efficacy%20of%20deep%20breathing%20exercises%2C%20which%20he%20said%20will%20provide%20immunity%20from%20viruses%20like%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chatterjee's%20four-and-a-half-minute%20documentary%20titled%20%26quot%3BBreathing%20for%20Good%20Health%26quot%3B%20starts%20with%20the%20recitation%20of%20the%20ancient%20Sanskrit%20symbol%20of%20%26quot%3BOm%26quot%3B%2C%20sitting%20shirtless%20on%20a%20frozen%20lake%20bed%20in%20Beijing%2C%20practising%20deep%20breathing%20workout%20followed%20by%20stomach%20churning%20and%20Sheersh%20Asan%2C%20the%20headstand%20exercise%20has%20gone%20viral%20in%20social%20media%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBreathing%20is%20the%20first%20thing%20we%20do%20when%20we%20come%20to%20the%20world%20and%20the%20last%20thing%20we%20do%20when%20we%20leave%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%20as%20he%20sets%20to%20begin%20the%20exercise%20in%20the%20sub-zero%20temperature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chatterjee%2C%2060%2C%20said%20when%20he%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20lead%20UN%20diplomat%20in%20China%20in%202020%2C%20he%20was%20close%20to%20obesity%20with%20high%20cholesterol%2C%20hypertension%2C%20and%20pre-diabetic%20with%20a%20high%20heart%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20high-intensity%20breathing%2C%20fasting%20and%20cold%20exposure%2C%20he%20lost%2025%20kgs%20while%20managing%20to%20attain%20normal%20blood%20pressure%20and%20other%20standard%20health%20parameters%20that%20helped%20him%20to%20achieve%20physical%20and%20mental%20equilibrium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chatterjee's%20appointment%20to%20head%2026%20UN%20offices%20in%20China%20made%20headlines%20as%20it%20came%20amid%20the%20India-China%20tensions%20over%20the%20eastern%20Ladakh%20standoff%20which%20is%20still%20unresolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chatterjee%2C%20whose%20family%20migrated%20to%20Kolkata%20during%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20went%20through%20a%20torrid%20childhood%20following%20the%20attack%20of%20polio%20and%20rose%20to%20be%20a%20decorated%20Indian%20military%20officer%20serving%20in%20the%20elite%20para%20regiment%20with%20postings%20in%20the%20Indian%20Peace%20Keeping%20Force%20(IPKF)%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20counter-insurgency%20operations%20in%20India's%20North%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20decorated%20for%20gallantry%20in%201995.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20three%20years%20I%20had%20polio%2C%20I%20still%20recall%20the%20electric%20shock%20treatment%20in%20the%20hospitals%20for%20the%20leg%20to%20reactivate%20it.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20he%20was%20among%20the%20fortunate%20ones%20who%20recovered%20completely%20from%20polio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20into%20the%20National%20Defence%20Academy%20(NDA)%20on%20the%20second%20attempt%20in%201981.%20It%20was%20a%20transformative%20moment%20for%20me%20and%20brought%20about%20a%20dramatic%20change%20as%20I%20became%20a%20polo%20player%2C%20and%20a%20boxer%20winning%20the%20best%20boxing%20title%20and%20many%20things%20changed.%20Graduated%20from%20NDA%2C%20I%20joined%20the%20elite%20para%20regiment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20he%20got%20a%20postgraduate%20degree%20from%20the%20Ivy%20League%20Princeton%20University%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20too%20has%20an%20India-China%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20heads%20the%20UN%20mission%20in%20China%20his%20wife%20Ban%20Hyun-Hee%20from%20South%20Korea%20is%20the%20chief%20of%20UNICEF%20social%20policy%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%2025-year%20UN%20diplomatic%20career%2C%20Mr%20Chatterjee%20served%20in%20Kenya%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20Denmark%2C%20Iraq%2C%20Somalia%2C%20South%20Sudan%2C%20Sudan%20(Darfur)%2C%20Indo