how-sports-betting-fantasy-games-taking-over-college-campuses-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egamble%20more%20than%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20they've%20been%20found%20to%20have%20lower%20levels%20of%20impulsive%20coping%20in%20gambling%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20precise%20reason%20for%20this%20behavior%20is%20hard%20to%20pin%20down%2C%20said%20Timothy%20Fong%2C%20a%20clinical%20professor%20of%20psychiatry%20at%20UCLA%20and%20the%20codirector%20of%20its%20gambling-studies%20program.%20There's%20a%20cultural%20component%3A%20In%20the%20'80s%2C%20young%20men%20were%20fed%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BWall%20Street%2C%26quot%3B%20shown%20flashy%20cars%20and%20money%2C%20and%20told%20that%20greed%20is%20good.%20In%20the%20'90s%20and%20early%202000s%2C%20they%20were%20sold%20on%20more%20traditional%20forms%20of%20gambling%20and%20poker.%20Now%20they're%20being%20marketed%20sports%20betting%20and%20crypto.%20But%20it%20also%20goes%20deeper%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20years%2C%20when%20we've%20studied%20gambling%20behaviors%20as%20well%20as%20other%20addictive%20behaviors%2C%20the%20trend%20has%20always%20been%20males%20more%20than%20females%20are%20impacted%2C%26quot%3B%20Fong%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20said%2C%20well%2C%20is%20that%20a%20biological%20risk%3F%20Is%20that%20a%20culturally%20driven%20risk%3F%20Is%20that%20a%20psychological%20risk%20or%20a%20social%20risk%20factor%3F%20And%20basically%2C%20what%20I%20can%20say%20is%20that%20it's%20probably%20a%20combination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20may%20be%20FOMO%2C%20as%20in%20fear%20of%20missing%20out.%20Younger%20men%20see%20their%20friends%20playing%20in%20crypto%20or%20betting%20on%20sports%2C%20and%20they%20want%20to%20join%20in.%20Many%20of%20them%20have%20income%20they're%20not%20doing%20more%20productive%20things%20with%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20pandemic%20that%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20consumers%20who%20were%20once%20trying%20to%20save%20up%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BEh%2C%20screw%20it.%26quot%3B%20Maybe%2040%20years%20ago%20a%2028-year-old%20had%20a%20mortgage%20and%20a%20family%20to%20support.%20Now%20he%20doesn't%20have%20those%20responsibilities%20and%20can%20direct%20disposable%20income%20toward%20whichever%20stock%20he%20just%20saw%20recommended%20on%20Reddit%20or%20a%20bet%20on%20whether%20the%20next%20pitch%20in%20a%20baseball%20game%20will%20be%20a%20ball%20or%20a%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKahlil%20Philander%2C%20a%20Washington%20State%20University%20professor%20who%20focuses%20on%20public%20policy%20and%20gambling%2C%20said%20this%20gambling%20boom%20is%20being%20compounded%20by%20a%20novelty%20effect.%20Many%20young%20people%20are%20being%20exposed%20to%20gambling%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20and%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20products%20are%20being%20marketed%20aggressively%20to%20them.%20All%20the%20advertising%20dollars%20that%20have%20been%20spent%20on%20sports-betting%20platforms%20and%20crypto%20exchanges%2C%20for%20example%2C%20have%20amplified%20the%20exposure%20effect.%20The%20other%20part%20of%20the%20story%20is%20that%20many%20of%20these%20people%20haven't%20gambled%20before%3A%20Unlike%20a%2060-year-old%20who's%20been%20there%2C%20done%20that%2C%20they%20haven't%20internalized%20the%20downsides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20are%20risks%20or%20risk-mitigating%20strategies%20that%20individuals%20can%20take%2C%20they%20might%20not%20have%20learned%20those%20lessons%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20Philander%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20can%20lead%20to%20higher%20levels%20of%20involvement%2C%20more%20harmful%20activity%2C%20all%20the%20types%20of%20things%20that%20people%20with%20more%20experience%20might%20have%20figured%20out%20for%20themselves%20one%20way%20or%20another.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20is%20technology%20is%20the%20idea%20that%20guys%20don't%20have%20to%20walk%20over%20to%20the%20casino%20to%20place%20a%20bet%20or%20call%20a%20broker%20to%20trade%20a%20stock%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20they%20can%20just%20take%20out%20their%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20technology%20that%20brings%20us%20that%20intersection%20between%20gambling%2C%20gaming%2C%20investing%2C%20and%20financial%20risk%2C%20that%20technology%20barrier%20is%20so%20low%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Fong%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20young%20men%2C%20a%20level%20of%20nihilism%20about%20the%20economy%20leads%20to%20an%20impetus%20to%20take%20some%20risks.%20It%20shows%20up%20in%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BDumb%20Money%2C%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20GameStop%20phenomenon%2C%20or%20%26quot%3BThis%20Is%20Not%20Financial%20Advice%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20documentary%20about%20dogecoin%20where%20the%20protagonists%20are%20portrayed%20as%20Davids%20against%20Goliaths%20%E2%80%94%20hedge%20funds%2C%20but%20also%20the%20economic%20system%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20at%20a%20place%20as%20a%20society%20where%20there%20are%20many%20new%20forms%20of%20gambling%20where%20the%20nature%20of%20investing%20and%20financial%20risk-taking%20is%20much%20different%20than%20it%20was%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Philander%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20investor%20Warren%20Buffett%2C%20who%20has%20a%20penchant%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fwarren-buffett-bitcoin-gambling-token-crypto-market-outlook-berkshire-hathaway-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoing%20some%20finger-wagging%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20described%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-letter-munger-berkshire-annual-shareholder-stock-speculation-ai-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20shifting%20nature%20of%20investing%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-hathaway-shareholder-letter-cash-stocks-portfolio-return-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletter%20to%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20whatever%20reasons%2C%20markets%20now%20exhibit%20far%20more%20casino-like%20behavior%20than%20they%20did%20when%20I%20was%20young%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20casino%20now%20resides%20in%20many%20homes%20and%20daily%20tempts%20the%20occupants.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20new%20customers%2C%20problem-gambling%20behavior%20is%20increasing%2C%20especially%20among%20young%20men.%20A%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsocialwork.rutgers.edu%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2023-10%2FPrevalence_Report_2023_Final.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20prevalence%20of%20gambling%20in%20New%20Jersey%20%E2%80%94%20where%20sports%20betting%20and%20online%20gambling%20are%20legal%2C%20and%20where%20Atlantic%20City%20is%20%E2%80%94%20found%20that%20men%20had%20double%20the%20rate%20of%20high-risk%20problem%20gambling%20than%20women%20and%20that%20those%20ages%2018%20to%2044%20were%20at%20the%20highest%20risk.%20The%20New%20Jersey%20report%20identified%20a%20significant%20prevalence%20of%20high-risk%20stock%20trading%20among%20young%20men.%20In%20the%20state%2C%20which%20pushed%20to%20have%20the%20federal%20law%20prohibiting%20sports%20betting%20overturned%2C%20calls%20to%20its%20problem-gambling%20hotline%20tripled%20in%20five%20years%2C%20with%20people%2025%20to%2034%20being%20the%20likeliest%20to%20reach%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20who%20gamble%20don't%20wind%20up%20with%20an%20addiction.%20According%20to%20the%20National%20Council%20on%20Problem%20Gambling%2C%20some%202.5%20million%20Americans%20have%20a%20severe%20gambling%20problem%2C%20and%20another%205%20million%20to%208%20million%20have%20a%20problem%20it%20considers%20mild%20or%20moderate.%20That's%20a%20small%20sliver%20of%20the%20population.%20Plenty%20of%20people%20do%20some%20amount%20of%20betting%20and%20eventually%20fall%20off%2C%20or%20they%20dip%20in%20from%20time%20to%20time%20and%20are%20just%20fine.%20The%20public's%20interest%20in%20crypto%20ebbs%20and%20flows%2C%20and%20just%20because%20someone%20got%20into%20meme%20stocks%20for%20a%20while%20doesn't%20mean%20they're%20living%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2F3-meme-stocks-that-r-wallstreetbets-loves-but-shouldnt-1033148653%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20Bets%3C%2Fa%3E%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20explosion%20of%20playing%20so%20much%20with%20money%20in%20the%20US%20is%20worrying%2C%20especially%20without%20a%20lot%20going%20on%20in%20the%20way%20of%20regulations%2C%20education%2C%20or%20safeguards%20to%20keep%20problem%20gambling%20in%20check.%20At%20least%20a%20sports-betting%20app%20will%20nudge%20someone%20to%20slow%20down%20if%20they%20go%20too%20far%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20virtually%20no%20protections%20in%20place%20if%20your%20day-trading%20habit%20gets%20out%20of%20hand%2C%20and%20many%20people%20don't%20even%20realize%20that%20what%20they're%20doing%20really%20is%20gambling.%20Fong%20told%20me%20he%20sees%20patients%20who%20will%20have%20lost%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20playing%20stocks%20and%20insist%20they%20just%20didn't%20time%20the%20market%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20one%20question%20I'll%20ask%20folks%2C%20I'll%20say%2C%20'Does%20this%20behavior%20make%20your%20life%20better%2C%20or%20does%20it%20create%20problems%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECasinos%2C%20sportsbooks%2C%20and%20trading%20platforms%20want%20to%20make%20money%20off%20bettors%2C%20and%20the%20way%20to%20do%20that%20is%20to%20get%20them%20to%20play%20more%2C%20not%20less.%20While%20many%20young%20men%20will%20eventually%20move%20on%20from%20their%20betting%20habits%2C%20not%20all%20of%20them%20will%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20company's%20hope%20is%20to%20turn%20them%20into%20clients%20for%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C