0Khan's%20Mumbai%20home%20after%20arresting%20the%20two%20suspects%20involved%20in%20the%20crime%20from%20Bhuj%20in%20Gujarat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20at%204%3A55%20am%2C%20two%20men%20on%20a%20motorcycle%20fired%20five%20rounds%20outside%20Galaxy%20Apartments%20in%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%2C%20where%20the%20actor%20resides%2C%20and%20fled%20from%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVicky%20Gupta%2C%2024%2C%20and%20Sagar%20Kumar%20Palak%2C%2021%20-%20both%20from%20West%20Champaran%20in%20Bihar%20-%20were%20arrested%20by%20Mumbai%20Police%20from%20the%20premises%20of%20a%20temple%20%C2%A0in%20Gujarat's%20Kutch%20district%20late%20Monday%20night.%C2%A0Deputy%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Kutch-West%2C%20Mahendra%20Bagadiya%2C%20confirmed%20that%20Gupta%20and%20Palak%20have%20confessed%20to%20their%20involvement%20in%20the%20firing%20incident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20accused%20conducted%20reconnaissance%20of%20Mr%20Khan's%20residence%20three%20times%20prior%20to%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20men%2C%20according%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20are%20part%20of%20the%20notorious%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang.%20Bishnoi%20is%20currently%20in%20Tihar%20Jail%20for%20his%20involvement%20in%20several%20high-profile%20murder%20cases%20including%20that%20of%20musician%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala%20and%20Rajput%20leader%20and%20Karni%20Sena%20chief%20Sukhdev%20Singh%20Gogamedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Were%20The%20Accused%20Caught%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20earlier%20investigation%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20indicated%20that%20the%20scheme%20originated%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20where%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%2C%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi's%20brother%2C%20entrusted%20the%20task%20of%20selecting%20shooters%20to%20Rohit%20Godara%2C%20another%20gangster%20also%20based%20in%20the%20US.%20This%20decision%20was%20likely%20influenced%20by%20Godara's%20extensive%20network%20of%20professional%20shooters%20spanning%20several%20states%20in%20India%2C%20police%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnmol%20Bishnoi%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20incident%20through%20a%20Facebook%20post.%20However%2C%20the%20IP%20address%20of%20the%20Facebook%20page%20that%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20firing%20incident%20was%20traced%20back%20to%20Canada.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20from%20five%20states%20-%20Maharashtra%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Haryana%2C%20and%20Punjab%20-%20initiated%20a%20coordinated%20effort%20to%20apprehend%20those%20involved.%20An%20FIR%20was%20registered%20and%20using%20CCTV%20footage%2C%20the%20police%20managed%20to%20piece%20together%20crucial%20evidence%20and%20strategies%20a%20plan%20to%20catch%20the%20accused.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVicky%20Gupta%20and%20Sagar%20Kumar%20Palak%20had%20been%20residing%20in%20a%20rented%20accommodation%20in%20Panvel%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Raigad.%20The%20two%20men%20had%20paid%20a%20deposit%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20for%20the%20house%20and%20had%20agreed%20to%20a%20monthly%20rent%20of%20Rs%203%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESagar%20Kumar%20Palak's%20prior%20stint%20in%20Haryana%20emerged%20as%20a%20focal%20point%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%20after%20reports%20of%20his%20affiliation%20with%20the%20notorious%20Bishnoi%20gang%20emerged.%20A%20multi-pronged%20approach%20was%20implemented%20in%20the%20search%20operation%20with%2012%20specialised%20teams%20formed%20to%20track%20down%20the%20accused.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeams%20were%20sent%20to%20Gujarat%20after%20the%20police%20suspected%20the%20accused%20might%20be%20hiding%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20police%20first%20reached%20Bhuj%20before%20travelling%2058%20km%20away%20to%20Nakhatrana%20where%20they%20caught%20the%20accused%20from%20a%20temple.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20accused%20were%20subsequently%20transported%20to%20Mumbai%20and%20presented%20before%20a%20magistrate%20court%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crime%20branch%20petitioned%20for%20a%2014-day%20custody%20of%20the%20suspects%2C%20citing%20the%20necessity%20for%20their%20interrogation%20to%20uncover%20details%20regarding%20the%20conspiracy%20and%20to%20identify%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20the%20whole%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20approved%20the%20police%20custody%20request%2C%20granting%20a%20period%20of%20nine%20days%20(until%20April%2025)%20for%20further%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713256440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F%2Fsalman-khan-ndtv-_625x300_1529317549085.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faccused-did-3-recces-of-salman-khans-house-fired-5-shots-mumbai-police-5453202%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20recces%20done%2C%20five%20shots%20fired%20-%20Mumbai%20Police%20today%20shared%20details%20of%20the%20sensational%20firing%20incident%20near%20Bollywood%20actor%20Salman%20Khan's%20Mumbai%20home%20after%20arresting%20the%20two%20suspects%20involved%20in%20the%20crime%20from%20Bhuj%20in%20Gujarat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faccused-did-3-recces-of-salman-khans-house-fired-5-shots-mumbai-police-5453202%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faccused-did-3-recces-of-salman-khans-house-fired-5-shots-mumbai-police-5453202%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faccused-did-3-recces-of-salman-khans-house-fired-5-shots-mumbai-police-5453202%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20About%20Benazir%20Bhutto's%20Daughter%20Aseefa%20Who%20Is%20Now%20A%20Pak%20Assembly%20Member%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbenazir-bhuttos-daughter-takes-oath-as-member-of-pakistan-assembly-5451755%5C%22%3EAseefa%20Bhutto-Zardari%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20made%20her%20political%20debut%20in%20Pakistan%20by%20taking%20her%20oath%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20the%20National%20Assembly%20(MNA)%20on%20Monday%20amidst%20chaos%20from%20opposition%20benches.%20She%20was%20elected%20unopposed%20from%20NA-207%20Shaheed%20Benazirabad%20on%20March%2029%20and%20filled%20the%20seat%20vacated%20by%20her%20father%2C%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%2C%20after%20his%20presidency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%20congratulating%20Aseefa%20Bhutto%20Zardari%20on%20taking%20the%20oath%20as%20Member%20of%20the%20National%20Assembly%2C%20in%20Islamabad%2C%26quot%3B%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPresOfPakistan%2Fstatus%2F1779881693647630591%5C%22%3Eposted%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Her%20oath%20was%20administered%20amid%20opposition%20from%20PTI-associated%20MNAs%2C%20who%20protested%20due%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20their%20NA-207%20candidate%2C%20Ghulam%20Mustafa%20Rind%2C%20claiming%20unfair%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20facts%20about%20Aseefa%20Bhutto-Zardari%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAseefa%20Bhutto%20Zardari%20was%20born%20in%20February%201993%20and%20is%20the%20youngest%20daughter%20of%20former%20Pakistan%20Prime%20Minister%20Benazir%20Bhutto%20(who%20was%20assassinated%20in%202007)%20and%20two-time%20Pakistan%20President%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari.%20Her%20brother%2C%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari%2C%20is%20the%20Chairman%20of%20PPP%20and%20served%20as%20the%20Minister%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20between%20April%202022%20and%20August%202023.%20Her%20aunt%20Dr%20Azra%20Fazal%20Pechuho%20is%20the%20former%20Sindh%20Health%20Minister.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20studied%20at%20Oxford%20Brookes%20University%2C%20University%20College%20London%2C%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Edinburgh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20made%20her%20political%20debut%20at%20a%20PPP%20rally%20in%202020%2C%20following%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20her%20family's%20political%20legacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20the%2014th%20President%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20reports%20claimed%20that%20Aseefa%20Bhutto%20Zardari%20could%20potentially%20be%20announced%20as%20Pakistan's%20First%20Lady.%20The%20title%20is%20typically%20given%20to%20the%20President's%20wife%20and%20she%20would%20receive%20the%20protocol%20and%20privileges%20befitting%20the%20First%20Lady.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20not%20been%20confirmed%20officially.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMs%20Bhutto-Zardari%20was%20the%20first%20baby%20in%20Pakistan%20to%20be%20vaccinated%20against%20polio.%20She%20is%20now%20the%20country's%20Ambassador%20for%20polio%20eradication.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713256380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F6rk6k31o_aseefa-bhutto-zardari_625x300_12_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpeople%2Faseefa-bhutto-zardari-all-about-benazir-bhuttos-daughter-who-is-now-a-member-of-pak-assembly-5453251%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aseefa%20Bhutto-Zardari%20has%20made%20her%20political%20debut%20in%20Pakistan%20by%20taking%20her%20oath%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20the%20National%20Assembly%20(MNA)%20on%20Monday%20amidst%20chaos%20from%20opposition%20benches.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpeople%2Faseefa-bhutto-zardari-all-about-benazir-bhuttos-daughter-who-is-now-a-member-of-pak-assembly-5453251%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpeople%2Faseefa-bhutto-zardari-all-about-benazir-bhuttos-daughter-who-is-now-a-member-of-pak-assembly-5453251%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpeople%2Faseefa-bhutto-zardari-all-about-benazir-bhuttos-daughter-who-is-now-a-member-of-pak-assembly-5453251%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nuclear%20accident%20'dangerously%20close'%20after%20Ukraine%20plant%20att