20age%20when%20global%20dysfunction%20is%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%2C%20the%20region's%20fissures%20are%20ready%20to%20explode%20in%20unprecedented%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong%20In%20The%20Making%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stage%20was%20set%20for%20the%20latest%20round%20of%20escalation%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20when%20Israel%20attacked%20Iran's%20embassy%20compound%20in%20Damascus%20two%20weeks%20back%2C%20killing%20two%20senior%20commanders%20of%20Iran's%20Islamic%20Revolution%20Guard%20Corps%20(IRGC)%20and%20their%20aides.%20This%20included%20Brig.%20Gen.%20Mohammad%20Reza%20Zahedi%2C%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20the%20Iranian%20operation%20to%20arm%20the%20Hezbollah.%20Iran%20put%20the%20blame%20quickly%20on%20Israel%20for%20the%20air%20strike%2C%20viewing%20it%20as%20a%20violation%20of%20its%20sovereignty%20and%20vowing%20retaliation.%20Iranian%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20had%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20Israel%20would%20be%20punished%20for%20the%20attack%2C%20while%20President%20Ebrahim%20Raisi%20had%20also%20underlined%20that%20Israeli%20actions%20would%20%26quot%3Bnot%20go%20unanswered%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20long%20time%2C%20Israel's%20focus%20had%20been%20on%20Iranian%20proxies%20as%20it%20sought%20to%20contain%20groups%20like%20Hezbollah%20without%20directly%20targeting%20Iran.%20Over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20Syria%20emerged%20as%20the%20central%20battleground%20for%20Tel%20Aviv%20and%20Tehran.%20During%20the%20recent%20Gaza%20crisis%2C%20Iranian%20proxies%20have%20been%20taking%20direct%20aim%20at%20Israel%2C%20which%20has%20been%20facing%20attacks%20from%20multiple%20fronts.%20Last%20week%2C%20Iran%20took%20its%20revenge%20when%20it%20launched%20around%20300%20drones%20and%20cruise%20and%20ballistic%20missiles%20at%20Israel%20in%20an%20unprecedented%20show%20of%20strength%2C%20but%20almost%20all%20of%20them%20were%20intercepted%20by%20Israeli%20air%20defences%20with%20significant%20support%20from%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20France%20and%20Jordan.%20Israel%20used%20its%20Aerial%20Defense%20Array%2C%20the%20three-tier%20umbrella%20of%20missile%20defence%20systems%2C%20to%20thwart%20the%20barrage%20of%20incoming%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20Allies%20Have%20Responded%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20critical%20issue%20before%20Israeli%20decision-makers%20now%20is%20to%20re-establish%20deterrence%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20Iran%2C%20with%20allies%20that%20helped%20in%20fending%20off%20the%20Iranian%20attack%20calling%20for%20restraint.%20The%20Biden%20administration%20has%20reportedly%20underscored%20to%20their%20Israeli%20counterparts%20that%20the%20US%20will%20not%20participate%20in%20any%20offensive%20action%20against%20Iran.%20The%20UK%2C%20while%20working%20with%20allies%20to%20%26quot%3Bde-escalate%26quot%3B%20the%20situation%2C%20also%20wants%20to%20ensure%20that%20its%20efforts%20are%20aimed%20at%20ensuring%20a%20pause%20in%20fighting%20and%20getting%20aid%20into%20Gaza.%20%26quot%3BWe%20must%20both%20be%20alongside%20Israel%20to%20ensure%20its%20security%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%20but%20call%20for%20a%20limit%20to%20avoid%20escalation%2C%26quot%3B%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20said%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20growing%20chorus%20for%20immediate%20de-escalation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20significant%20are%20the%20regional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-israel-conflict-israel-jordan-relations-why-jordan-which-slammed-israel-over-gaza-stepped-in-to-stop-iran-drones-5445958%5C%22%3Eplayers%20such%20as%20Jordan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20which%2C%20in%20their%20own%20ways%2C%20have%20helped%20Israel%20and%20would%20now%20want%20Tel%20Aviv%20to%20take%20their%20interests%20into%20account%20as%20well.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20pressure%20on%20the%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20government%20to%20respond%20continues%20to%20be%20high%2C%20particularly%20from%20his%20own%20base.%20Israel%20has%20maintained%20that%20the%20confrontation%20with%20Iran%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20over%20yet%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20Iran%20has%20warned%20Israel%20that%20its%20response%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20much%20larger%20than%20tonight's%20military%20action%20if%20Israel%20retaliates%20against%20Iran%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20Over%20Yet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETehran%20moved%20fast%20after%20the%20attack%20to%20telegraph%20the%20message%20that%20its%20response%20had%20been%20effective%20and%20successful%2C%20so%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20do%20anything%20more%20at%20this%20stage.%20Iran's%20joint%20chief%20of%20staff%20declared%3A%20%26quot%3BThank%20God%2C%20we%20see%20this%20mission%20as%20a%20successful%20one%20that%20brought%20the%20necessary%20results%2C%20so%20we%20see%20no%20need%20to%20pursue%20it%20any%20further.%26quot%3B%20This%20was%20Iran%20telling%20the%20world%20that%20it%20was%20willing%20to%20be%20measured%20in%20its%20response%20and%20has%20no%20intent%20to%20escalate%20further.%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20has%20been%20suggesting%20that%20it%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-israel-war-israel-says-it-would-exact-price-from-iran-when-time-is-right-10-points-5443725%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bexact%20a%20price%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20time%20and%20place%20of%20its%20choosing%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20country%20that%20had%20lost%20its%20sense%20of%20security%20after%20the%20Hamas-led%20assault%20on%20October%207%20last%20year%2C%20Israel%20had%20been%20meandering%20along%20under%20the%20now-discredited%20leadership%20of%20Netanyahu%2C%20who%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20restore%20confidence%20with%20his%20seemingly%20unending%20war%20in%20Gaza%20and%20a%20growing%20global%20isolation%20for%20Israel.%20The%20success%20in%20tackling%20the%20Iranian%20attack%20last%20week%20should%20be%20leveraged%20by%20Tel%20Aviv%20in%20shaping%20a%20new%20compact%20with%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi's%20Challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%2C%20however%2C%20continues%20to%20wait%20with%20bated%20breath%20for%20the%20next%20move%20in%20this%20dangerous%20game%20of%20one-upmanship.%20New%20Delhi%2C%20too%2C%20is%20getting%20caught%20in%20the%20quagmire%2C%20given%20that%2017%20of%20the%2025%20crew%20members%20on%20the%20MSC%20Aries%20-%20a%20commercial%20ship%20with%20links%20to%20Israel%20that%20was%20captured%20by%20Iran%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20the%20UAE%20last%20week%20-%20are%20Indian.%20New%20Delhi%20has%20called%20for%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20de-escalation%2C%20exercise%20of%20restraint%2C%20stepping%20back%20from%20violence%20and%20return%20to%20the%20path%20of%20diplomacy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20rightfully%20proud%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20has%20been%20able%20to%20manage%20good%20ties%20with%20all%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20-%20Iran%2C%20Israel%20and%20the%20Arab%20states.%20It%20has%20key%20interests%20to%20pursue%20with%20all%20three.%20Because%20of%20this%2C%20Iran%20has%20allowed%20Indian%20diplomats%20to%20meet%20the%20Indian%20crew%20members%20of%20the%20seized%20cargo%20vessel.%20But%20as%20tensions%20continue%20to%20be%20high%20in%20an%20ever-volatile%20region%2C%20this%20balancing%20act%20of%20India%20will%20get%20tougher%20and%20Indian%20diplomacy%20will%20have%20to%20be%20in%20full%20gear%20to%20limit%20the%20costs%20of%20escalation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20His%20most%20recent%20books%20include%20'India%20and%20the%20Gulf%3A%20Theoretical%20Perspectives%20and%20Policy%20Shifts'%20(Cambridge%20University%20Press)%20and%20'Politics%20and%20Geopolitics%3A%20Decoding%20India's%20Neighbourhood%20Challenge'%20(Rupa)%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E