o%20abroad%20for%20an%20undergraduate%20degree%2C%20which%20was%20quite%20unheard%20of%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardika%20worked%20summers%20after%20finishing%20Class%2010%2C%20where%20her%20first%20job%20was%20working%20as%20a%20market%20researcher%20for%20shampoo%20fragrances.%20After%20that%2C%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20font%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20before%20going%20to%20college%2C%20I%20had%20to%20create%20fonts%20for%20Indian%20languages%20on%20the%20computer.%20Since%20they%20wanted%20someone%20who%20could%20handle%20computers%20and%20had%20an%20artistic%20mind%2C%20I%20got%20the%20job%20and%20worked%20there%20for%20three%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346774%2Fbengaluru-residents-saving-water-scarcity-rainwater-harvesting-recycle-greywayer-aerators-restrictors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBengaluru%20resident.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hardika%20started%20Kinara%20Capital%20in%202011%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347263%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHardika%20started%20Kinara%20Capital%20in%202011%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20managed%20her%20pocket%20money%2C%20raising%20funds%20for%20her%20undergraduate%20degree%20in%20the%20US%20was%20no%20mean%20feat.%20Hardika%20shares%20that%20she%20spent%20almost%2018%20months%20preparing%20for%20all%20the%20different%20exams%2C%20but%20mostly%20just%20trying%20to%20find%20avenues%20for%20her%20finances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20really%20not%20cheap%20to%20go%20to%20the%20US%20in%20the%2080s.%20Liberal%20arts%20colleges%20then%20gave%20some%20financial%20aid%2C%20but%20it%20was%20very%20limited%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20parents%20came%20to%20her%20rescue%20and%20sold%20their%20house%20to%20fund%20her%20education%2C%20moving%20to%20a%20smaller%20rented%20apartment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20then%20teenager%20entered%20Knox%20College%20in%20Illinois%2C%20USA%2C%20where%20she%20pursued%20a%20BA%20in%20computer%20science.%20The%20degree%20gave%20her%20the%20opportunity%20to%20study%20everything%20from%20world%20history%2C%20anthropology%2C%20economics%20to%20symbolic%20logic%20apart%20from%20traditional%20subjects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20undergraduate%20degree%2C%20she%20worked%20at%20Accenture%20in%20Chicago%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Sydney%2C%20and%20then%20back%20again%20in%20the%20US%20in%20San%20Francisco%20in%20financial%20services%2C%20technology%20and%20consulting%20for%20almost%2019%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20work%20also%20brought%20her%20to%20India%20almost%2010%20years%20later%2C%20in%20the%20post%20liberalisation%20era.%20For%20someone%20working%20in%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20she%20found%20a%20stark%20difference%20and%20a%20big%20gap%20in%20accessibility%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20filled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20decided%20to%20spend%20her%20weekends%20every%20summer%20as%20a%20social%20impact%20business%20mentor.%C2%A0%