2%80%9CThe%20rows%20in%20which%20saplings%20are%20to%20be%20planted%20must%20be%20in%20the%20direction%20from%20east%20to%20west%2C%20per%20the%20wind%20in%20the%20region%2C%20so%20that%20saplings%20do%20not%20get%20uprooted%20in%20storms.%20Also%2C%20saplings%20are%20planted%20at%20least%20one%20foot%20deep%20into%20the%20ground.%20We%20keep%20the%20distance%20of%2010%C3%9710%20feet%20between%20saplings%20and%20rows.%20Also%2C%20lemons%20thrive%20in%20soil%20that%20has%20a%20pH%20between%206%20and%207%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnand%20says%20he%20adopted%20the%20low-cost%20and%20high-profitability%20approach%20to%20growing%20lemons%20and%20placed%2050%20plants%20of%20%3Cem%3Emosambi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sweet%20lime)%20among%20400%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F205409%2Forganic-farming-rajasthan-earning-lakhs-lemons-pickle-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elemon%20trees%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20he%20uses%20both%20organic%20and%20inorganic%20ways%20to%20fertilise%20the%20soil%20and%20control%20pest%20attacks.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20monsoon%2C%20I%20add%2015%20kg%20of%20compost%20to%20every%20tree%20to%20get%20a%20good%20yield.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20I%20add%20fertilisers%20like%20DAP%2C%20urea%2C%20and%20potash.%20Although%20no%20chemicals%20are%20used%20in%20natural%20farming%2C%20we%20were%20forced%20to%20use%20chemicals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FLemon-farming-3-1712930272.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22More%20than%20the%20huge%20profits%2C%20Anand%20finds%20contentment%20in%20leading%20a%20stress-free%20life%20in%20the%20village.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FLemon-farming-3-1712930272.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FLemon-farming-3-1712930272-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FLemon-farming-3-1712930272-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FLemon-farming-3-1712930272-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FLemon-farming-3-1712930272-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347235%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20the%20huge%20profits%2C%20Anand%20finds%20contentment%20in%20leading%20a%20stress-free%20life%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20in%20minor%20fungal%20and%20pest%20attacks%2C%20we%20spray%20organic%20pesticides%20prepared%20using%20cow%20urine%2C%20jaggery%2C%20garlic%2C%20and%20chillies%20paste.%20This%20mixture%20needs%20to%20be%20sprayed%20at%20a%20gap%20of%20two%20to%20three%20days.%20But%20when%20the%20damage%20on%20leaves%20is%20beyond%20control%2C%20we%20use%20permitted%20amounts%20of%20pesticides%20like%20chlorpyrifos.%20We%20only%20need%20to%20spray%20it%20once%20in%20a%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20about%20four%20years%20to%20bear%20fruits%20in%20lemon%20farms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Anand%20says%20he%20harvested%20400%20crates%20(or%20100%20tonnes)%20of%20lemons%2C%20which%20were%20sold%20between%20Rs%2040%20and%20Rs%2070%20in%20the%20local%20market.%20Interestingly%2C%20lemon%20farming%20also%20ensures%20a%20continuous%20inflow%20of%20income%20to%20Anand%20as%20lemons%20are%20in%20demand%20throughout%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%201.85%20lakh%2C%20today%2C%20Anand%20reaps%20profits%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%207%20lakh%20on%20his%20two%20acres%20of%20land.%20More%20than%20the%20huge%20profits%2C%20the%2050-year-old%20finds%20contentment%20in%20leading%20a%20stress-free%20life%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20regret%20quitting%20my%20well-paying%20job.%20Earlier%2C%20I%20was%20a%20servant%20to%20a%20company%2C%20now%20I%20am%20a%20proud%20owner%20of%20a%20farm.%20I%20feel%20%3Cem%3Ethehrao%20%3C%2Fem%3E(composure)%20in%20the%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Anand%20Mishra.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713166036000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347227%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Observing%20the%20year-round%20demand%20for%20lemons%2C%20Anand%20Mishra%20switched%20from%20growing%20traditional%20crops%20like%20wheat%2C%20paddy%2C%20and%20peas%20to%20cultivating%20lemons%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20With%20his%20two-acre%20farm%20now%20yielding%20Rs%207%20lakh%20in%20profits%2C%20he%20explains%20the%20reasoning%20behind%20this%20'unconventional'%20change.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347227%2Ffarmer-lemon-man-of-raebareli-uttar-pradesh-anand-mishra-earning-five-times-more-in-lakhs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Grow%20Pepper%2C%20Clove%2C%20Turmeric%20%26amp%3B%2015%20Types%20of%20Indian%20Spices%20At%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELocated%20close%20to%20the%20foothills%20of%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20Roorkee-based%20Dr%20Anshu%20Rathi%E2%80%99s%20kitchen%20smells%20heavenly.%20From%20cumin%E2%80%99s%20earthy%20aroma%20to%20refreshing%20fennel%20and%20pungent%20fenugreek%20seeds%20%E2%80%93%20her%20kitchen%20evokes%20the%20rustic%20charm%20of%20Indian%20spices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20crush%20%3Cem%3Ekasuri%20methi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(dried%20fenugreek%20leaves)%20on%20my%20palms%2C%20it%20leaves%20a%20very%20strong%20and%20tantalising%20smell.%20My%20husband%20is%20in%20awe%20of%20the%20fennel%20tea%20that%20I%20make.%20It%20feels%20so%20refreshing%20and%20tasty%20as%20it%20does%20not%20have%20any%20preservatives%20and%20colours%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Anshu%20(36)%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20doctor%20by%20profession%2C%20she%20has%20established%20a%20lavish%20garden%20of%20up%20to%20400%20plants%20of%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%20herbs%2C%20and%20spices%20on%20her%201%2C500-square-foot%20terrace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F63695%2Fherb-garden-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedicinal%20herbs%20%3C%2Fa%3Elike%20%3Cem%3Eashwagandha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20basil%2C%20and%20oregano%2C%20she%20grows%2015%20kinds%20of%20spices%20%E2%80%94%20including%20turmeric%2C%20black%20pepper%2C%20saffron%2C%20cloves%2C%20nutmeg%2C%20fennel%2C%20fenugreek%2C%20bay%20leaf%2C%20cinnamon%2C%20asafoetida%2C%20allspice%20plant%20(%3Cem%3Ekabab%20chini%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20chilli%2C%20coriander%2C%20nigella%20sativa%20plant%20(%3Cem%3Ekalonji%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20and%20cardamom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%20how%20to%20easily%20grow%20these%20Indian%20spices%20at%20home%2C%20some%20of%20which%20can%20be%20grown%20using%20ingredients%20available%20in%20the%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FGardening-2-1712929222.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Anshu%20grows%2015%20kinds%20of%20spices%20%E2%80%94%20including%20turmeric%2C%20fennel%2C%20and%20fenugreek.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FGardening-