ls%20that%20Shalini%20prepares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20lots%20of%20edible%20weeds%20growing%20on%20the%20property.%20So%2C%20my%20favourite%20thing%20is%20to%20pick%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20what%20is%20growing%20in%20the%20garden.%20Locally%2C%20they%20grow%20%3Cem%3Eurad%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(black%20gram)%20and%20make%20little%20dried%20%3Cem%3Ebadis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(vegetable%20nuggets)%20out%20of%20it%20for%20winter%2C%20because%20nothing%20grows%20here%20in%20the%20cold%20weather.%20So%2C%20they%20dry%20whatever%20they%20grow%20in%20summer%20or%20make%20these%20%3Cem%3Ebadis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20keep%20them.%20I%20love%20serving%20my%20guests%20these%20%3Cem%3Ebadis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20zucchini-based%20dishes%20because%20it%20grows%20here%20in%20abundance.%20We%20prepare%20it%20in%20various%20ways.%20There%20are%20also%20local%20dishes%20like%20%3Cem%3Esiddu%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20is%20like%20a%20bao%20stuffed%20with%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShalini%20also%20uses%20fiddlehead%20fern%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F248547%2Fhomemade-pickles-athey-nallatha-hafez-rahman-akshay-raveendran-kerala-homemakers-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20pickles%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealong%20with%20other%20produce%20like%20persimmon%20%3Cem%3Eachar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20plum%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20peach%20jam%2C%20and%20quince%20jam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20homestay%20steeped%20in%20sustainability%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitin%20is%20the%20one%20who%20handles%20all%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ejugaads%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(an%20innovative%20way%20of%20problem-solving)%20as%20Shalini%20puts%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitin%20informs%20that%20the%20homestay%20was%20made%20keeping%20in%20mind%20that%20it%20does%20not%20disturb%20the%20nature%20around.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20implemented%20a%20lot%20of%20eco-friendly%20and%20sustainable%20practices%20right%20from%20the%20design%20of%20the%20place.%20We%20also%20wanted%20to%20minimise%20our%20energy%20requirements.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20we%20started%20from%20the%20architecture%20and%20planning%20phase%2C%20where%20we%20utilised%20natural%20ways%20of%20heating%20and%20maximised%20sunlight%20exposure%20during%20winter%20while%20minimising%20it%20in%20summer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-10-1-1712578444.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%20offers%20delicious%20meals%20like%20siddu%2C%20badi%2C%20and%20homemade%20pickles.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-10-1-1712578444.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-10-1-1712578444-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-10-1-1712578444-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-10-1-1712578444-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-10-1-1712578444-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346808%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20offers%20delicious%20meals%20like%20siddu%2C%20badi%2C%20and%20homemade%20pickles.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20construction%20materials%2C%20most%20buildings%20in%20the%20hills%20are%20built%20with%20wood%20as%20it%20is%20a%20good%20insulating%20material.%20%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20incorporated%20insulating%20blocks%20in%20the%20construction%2C%20which%20further%20reduce%20heating%20and%20air%20conditioning%20costs.%20These%20blocks%20are%20light%20enough%20to%20float%20on%20water%20and%20insulate%20the%20entire%20building.%20Furthermore%2C%20all%20windows%20are%20double-glazed%20with%20argon%20gas%20in%20between%20for%20additional%20insulation%2C%20and%20the%20roofs%20are%20insulated%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20heating%2C%20the%20property%20utilises%20geothermal%20heat%20pumps%2C%20tapping%20into%20a%20spring%20on%20the%20property%20for%20ground%20source%20water.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20water%2C%20naturally%20warm%20in%20winter%2C%20is%20cycled%20through%20the%20geothermal%20heat%20pump%20to%20extract%20heat%2C%20which%20is%20then%20used%20to%20heat%20the%20building.%20Underfloor%20pipes%2C%20spanning%20almost%20a%20kilometre%2C%20distribute%20this%20heat%20throughout%20the%20building%2C%20providing%20an%20efficient%20heating%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nitin%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20faced%20several%20power%20cuts%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20be%20more%20sustainable%20and%20go%20solar.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20run%20our%20operations%20entirely%20on%20solar%20power.%20We%20have%20a%20solar%20system%20in%20place%20that%20generates%20electricity%2C%20and%20our%20entire%20house%20runs%20on%20this.%20Even%20on%20days%20when%20there%E2%80%99s%20as%20little%20as%2030%25%20sunlight%2C%20the%20system%20works%20efficiently.%20Additionally%2C%20any%20excess%20energy%20generated%20during%20the%20day%20is%20stored%20in%20batteries%2C%20which%20we%20then%20use%20for%20power%20backup%20when%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20six%20years%20of%20operations%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20hosted%20countless%20number%20of%20happy%20guests%20so%20far.%20Among%20them%20is%20Mumbai-based%20Priyanka%20who%20stayed%20at%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLocated%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Beas%20River%2C%20Shalini%20and%20Nitin%E2%80%99s%20homestay%20exceeded%20all%20our%20expectations.%20Surrounded%20by%20beautiful%20fruit%20trees%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20season%20you%20visit%2C%20you%20can%20indulge%20in%20farm-fresh%20fruits%20every%20day!%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsIpyiWSH3A%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsIpyiWSH3A%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsIpyiWSH3A%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Raison%20D'%C3%AAtre%20%7C%20Riverfront%20Homestay%20(%40raisondetremanali)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20goes%20on%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20food%20we%20experienced%20here%20was%20truly%20exceptional%2C%20offering%20some%20of%20the%20finest%20and%20freshest%20meals%20we%E2%80%99ve%20ever%20had%20%E2%80%94%20things%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20find%20back%20home.%20Throughout%20our%20f