2C%20the%20two%20have%20built%20HearNU%20%E2%80%94%20a%20hearing%20aid%20that%20uses%20bone%20conduction%20technology%2C%20offering%20a%20non-surgical%20solution%20for%20people%20with%20conductive%20hearing%20loss.%20They%20have%20also%20developed%20bone%20conduction%20earphones%20called%20WeHear%20OX%20%E2%80%94%20where%20the%20earphone%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20sit%20inside%20your%20ears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeHear%20has%20a%20granted%20patent%20for%20its%20HearNU%20and%20is%20transforming%20the%20lives%20of%20thousands%20of%20young%20children%20and%20adults%20with%20conductive%20hearing%20loss%2C%20in%20which%20sound%20waves%20are%20not%20able%20to%20carry%20all%20the%20way%20through%20to%20the%20inner%20ear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanishka%20and%20Raj%20claim%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20only%20bone-conduction%20hearing%20aid%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20Since%20their%20launch%20in%202021%2C%20they%20have%20sold%20over%2011%2C500%20devices%20and%20have%20earned%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%205.5%20crore%20in%20FY%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20bagged%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%202.5%20crore%20in%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20Season%203%20from%20Peyush%20Bansal%2C%20valuing%20their%20company%20at%20Rs%20250%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20exactly%20is%20bone%20conduction%20technology%20and%20what%20makes%20their%20patented%20product%20unique%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMade%20in%20India%20for%20the%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kanishka%20and%20Raj%20founded%20WeHear%20in%202021%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.